oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jim Sanders' Ranch Girls (incomplete take)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Incomplete take of Jim Sanders' Ranch Girls radio program. Featuring Jim Sanders playing characters Alexander and Ebenezer Snodgrass (unconfirmed), and Ranch Girls Helen Fox (fiddle) and Rusty Wright (vocals). Circa 1941.
